name: Borbins of the Midnight Clasp
description: Hailing from the Bogs of the <Anuran Countryside>, the Borbins of the Midnight Clasp are known for their skill in shadow magic. Specifically moving from shadow and shadow, smuggling goods within the shadows of clueless civilians. Now, after unfurling a cursed scroll and discovering secrets few others in Kharth know, they look towards the future with a glint in their eye. Their future is bright. The only question: what comes next?
